methods are functions used inside of a class.
(function --> a block of code that performs a certain task when called.)

---this - a keyword used inside a class i.e Vue, so that it calls on other variables used in the class.

**asynchronous and synchronous operations
**axios --> a javascript library used to send and receive requests.

